    oc:differentia "provides 10 proven, reusable hook configuration patterns for common Claude Code hook use cases including security validation, test enforcement, context loading, notification logging, MCP monitoring, build verification, permission confirmation, code quality checks, flag-based activation, and configuration-driven behavior" ;
